Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对机动  Bloody  Murder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快避开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹  往上跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安可儿  我给你一次解释的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟敢对直人大人发起攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,即便你是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不给我一个合理的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就把你彻底破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,安可儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹  跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快把安可儿破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,琉兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在的运作不正常
